{
  "stem": "23626.6",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We really were completely unaware how many of us are left.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We didn't know that so few are left.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But there was some kind of, like, I would call it electricity in the air, you know?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And also I remember, prior to it, it was Schindler's birthday.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was, like, a couple of months of-- before-- before the end of the war.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And somebody baked a cake.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I know they did, because we were singing Happy Birthday to him.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he was-- made a speech, you know, with his hands open, and was telling us that we are in a safe place, that no one can hurt us here.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There is no war going on here.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But also, he told us to stay in a silence for our people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "For our dead people.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because, prior to it, there was-- I only found out this after the war-- supposedly there was a transport that was stopped-- excuse me-- [PAUSES FOR 8 SECONDS] [DRINKS] they brought a transport to the front of the camp, and the SS told Schindler, if he doesn't take those people, they're going to open the door and kill them all and leave them there.",
      "word_count": 64
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was a transport of people that was on their way for 14 days.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And Schindler said, OK, I take 'em.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "What happened, they opened the doors.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Most of them were frozen dead inside.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The some that were alive were like skeleton.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And Schindler had-- some of our boys, supposedly, helped them to carry them and bring them, sort of, health-- whatever they could help them with.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Supposedly Mrs.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Schindler brought a lot of medication to help those few that survived.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But some of them that were dead, Schindler had obtained a plot for those to be buried in the Jewish tradition.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
